<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="B客戶">
  <data key="d0">B客戶</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">B客户, also referred to as B客戶, is an entity or organization that receives ongoing maintenance support and services. The term "B客户" emphasizes their role as a customer or client who consistently receives such services. Maintenance records detailing all interactions and activities related to B客户的 maintenance needs are meticulously documented by the service provider. These records include comprehensive information about various maintenance activities and service details, ensuring a thorough history of B客户的 maintenance support over time.

The descriptions highlight that B客户 is an organization for which maintenance records are kept, documenting every interaction and activity pertinent to their maintenance requirements. This documentation process covers not only interactions but also service details and various maintenance activities conducted on behalf of the client. The consistent use of detailed records underscores the importance placed on maintaining a thorough history of all support provided to B客户 over an extended period.

Overall, B客戶 is characterized as an entity that receives ongoing maintenance services with meticulous record-keeping practices by the service provider covering every aspect related to their maintenance needs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-412e17859c430b9ce8b929bc152053ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0d3b88d3601a1081c8354e0ef27952f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6e1908b68b82814f06780675f7938b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39206ec5906f23d68e051b1df74d3ca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c3e0271089b72556be831ea38a055f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5</data>
