  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">FISAC資料收容refers to a task related to data collection and submission for FISAC, which is currently in progress.&lt;SEP&gt;An ongoing process of collecting data for FISAC, involving IP application submissions.&lt;SEP&gt;This is a pending event for data storage with FISAC.&lt;SEP&gt;FISAC資料收容-進行中involves ongoing data containment procedures related to the FISAC system.&lt;SEP&gt;#fisac数据接收正在进行中。&lt;SEP&gt;FISAC資料收容-進行中describes ongoing efforts to manage and secure data within FISAC.</data>
