  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Centos作業系統升級refers to a planned upgrade of the CentOS operating system that is currently under assessment.&lt;SEP&gt;An assessment for upgrading the CentOS operating system, which is pending.&lt;SEP&gt;A pending evaluation process for upgrading the CentOS operating system.&lt;SEP&gt;An assessment of the CentOS operating system upgrade is currently being considered.&lt;SEP&gt;Centos作業系統升級is a pending system upgrade task being evaluated for Linux machines.&lt;SEP&gt;#centos操作系统升级(评估中)。</data>
