<node id="Carbon-Fiber Spikes">
  <data key="d0">Carbon-Fiber Spikes</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Carbon-Fiber Spikes are advanced sprinting shoes designed specifically for athletes competing in events such as the 100m sprint. Made primarily from carbon fiber, a material renowned for its lightweight and durable properties, these shoes offer runners an edge in terms of both speed and stability, making them crucial equipment for high-level competitive events. Carbon-Fiber Spikes provide enhanced speed and traction during races, which is essential for optimal performance on the track. Notable athletes such as Noah Carter have used these shoes to break records; specifically, Carter utilized Carbon-Fiber Spikes to set a new 100m sprint record at the World Athletics Championship. The primary purpose of these shoes is to enhance an athlete's performance by combining advanced materials with engineering innovations that improve both speed and stability during high-intensity races. These innovative features make Carbon-Fiber Spikes a key component in achieving peak athletic performance for competitive runners.&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes are advanced sprinting shoes that provide enhanced speed and traction.&lt;SEP&gt;Advanced sprinting shoes made from carbon fiber that provide enhanced speed and traction.&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes are advanced sprinting shoes that provide enhanced speed and traction.&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes are advanced sprinting shoes used by Noah Carter to enhance performance during the 100m sprint at the World Athletics Championship.&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes are advanced sprinting shoes used by Noah Carter to enhance performance during the race.&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes are advanced sprinting shoes that provide enhanced speed and traction.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfcf7e8f6051fb59b7f2cec85fa4dc4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d02e98febcd8f8650bbe77d789a41d69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17b29d261b8bce3ef9105d1c8a78415d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-345e520afd2a192e25824abb33740d46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-726c374f489423e007bce76f7810b46e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-886b4b629f3088ef8656c792cf7b3e8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-67cc5a5ed7a1cbea5f9e6d5f5d08ab51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcc4bf66788ce00c23c3e736753ea50a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-068ca517cbebf973fd4089bd45ef615c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-082efb5c18d778427dcd94905e5f4370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5096c0cdf6972a3670732e4f9be1d36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5479196dee25b34d077c01190c6c728b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a83bcdf6e7b7269cfd17b4f21457de8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39206ec5906f23d68e051b1df74d3ca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a81645d1d338ac013fa594b14c35640&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c4967b23b72f04d5c4ef37149d21ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0640212d45b4b92d91d0255cf90edf96&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c3e0271089b72556be831ea38a055f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6f1e5469f6278ea8a34bff96b293b69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e7cec156f57837e8d25cbe83a6db45f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6839b81653aa7c9b7ec794f3447380&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6caccf00501b5f4caf06dcfc047ae9e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5930b403906ecb929487592cef5210f2</data>
