<node id="C客戶">
  <data key="d0">C客戶</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">C客戶 is a client for whom detailed maintenance records are systematically maintained. These clients can be either individuals or organizations, and the records document all maintenance activities provided to them, including both past services conducted and ongoing support activities. The purpose of maintaining these records is to ensure comprehensive service tracking and continued support for C客戶.

The descriptions indicate that maintenance records for C客戶 include various aspects such as work carried out, documentation of ongoing maintenance tasks, and historical service provision details. These records are crucial for ensuring that all necessary information about the services provided to C客戶 is systematically managed and easily accessible.

Additionally, one description specifies that "C клиент является объектом обслуживания, для которого зарегистрирована запись о техническом обслуживании," which means that maintenance records for C клиент (equivalent to C客戶) are registered, indicating ongoing service activities. This further emphasizes the importance of systematic record-keeping for C客戶.

Overall, C客戶 refers to a client entity—whether individual or organization—for whom comprehensive and detailed maintenance records are maintained to document all aspects of technical support and services provided over time.&lt;SEP&gt;C客戶is the customer for whom maintenance records are being documented.&lt;SEP&gt;C客戶is an organization for which maintenance records are kept.&lt;SEP&gt;C客戶is the organization for which maintenance work was recorded.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3f8775862e3b8ea072578967e7520445&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-15d6c505e6a20b598aa21d52b466adcd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8ec2739edb4ee1ccc4cf68534e90be5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cdd29ae3537f38a27c3848632ad51359&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab226f704fc1b4d45dd06222f40cb39f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-068ca517cbebf973fd4089bd45ef615c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-082efb5c18d778427dcd94905e5f4370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9e37e8f7e8a98183b1724c16ce814a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d3d3acb3c191c9e65fac21b5ed9284f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5479196dee25b34d077c01190c6c728b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ff26e3a56f4aaf4bbd7c0dfae03685b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2fe3f974e54dd1f1ad98289cc79980d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c41e50d3a458388dc7fe53ece68ee69f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c1fca5402ff2eb1c53222e1d4db282a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e7cec156f57837e8d25cbe83a6db45f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6caccf00501b5f4caf06dcfc047ae9e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5930b403906ecb929487592cef5210f2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
