</node>
<node id="B人員">
  <data key="d0">B人員</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">B人員 is an engineer with a primary responsibility of performing and managing various maintenance activities, specifically for clients such as C客戶 and D客户. This role encompasses both the practical execution of maintenance work and the documentation and record-keeping related to these tasks. B人員 oversees the entire maintenance process from start to finish, ensuring that all necessary work is completed to maintain operational efficiency and that records are accurate and up-to-date. The duties involve handling a range of activities including conducting maintenance tasks for C客戶 and maintaining detailed records of all maintenance processes. Additionally, B人员 was also responsible for handling the maintenance service for another entity, which suggests multiple instances where B人員 has been assigned similar but distinct roles involving different clients or specific systems.&lt;SEP&gt;B персонал также является инженером по обслуживанию, участвующим в техническом обслуживании C клиента.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the engineer who handled the maintenance work for C客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;B人员is the engineer responsible for handling the maintenance work.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the engineer responsible for handling the maintenance record.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the engineer responsible for handling the maintenance tasks.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3f8775862e3b8ea072578967e7520445&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-15d6c505e6a20b598aa21d52b466adcd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8ec2739edb4ee1ccc4cf68534e90be5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f0773b8daffa7a65254a73867e36afb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cdd29ae3537f38a27c3848632ad51359&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab226f704fc1b4d45dd06222f40cb39f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-068ca517cbebf973fd4089bd45ef615c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-082efb5c18d778427dcd94905e5f4370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9e37e8f7e8a98183b1724c16ce814a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d3d3acb3c191c9e65fac21b5ed9284f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5479196dee25b34d077c01190c6c728b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ff26e3a56f4aaf4bbd7c0dfae03685b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2fe3f974e54dd1f1ad98289cc79980d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c41e50d3a458388dc7fe53ece68ee69f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a81645d1d338ac013fa594b14c35640&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c1fca5402ff2eb1c53222e1d4db282a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e7cec156f57837e8d25cbe83a6db45f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6caccf00501b5f4caf06dcfc047ae9e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5930b403906ecb929487592cef5210f2</data>
