<edge source="B客戶" target="A人員">
  <data key="d7">14.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(A人员, B客户) refers to a relationship where A人员 is responsible for providing various maintenance and technical support services to B客户. Specifically, A人员 handles the maintenance work of B客户的 system and ensures that it operates smoothly. This includes performing routine checks, addressing any issues that arise, and offering technical assistance as needed. On specific dates and times, A人員 provides maintenance services directly to B客戶 according to scheduled plans or when required by B客户's needs.

A人员 not only offers maintenance but also technical support, ensuring that the systems operated by B客户 function effectively without disruptions. This comprehensive service includes both proactive measures like regular system checks and responsive actions such as resolving problems promptly whenever they occur.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員performs maintenance services for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員conducts maintenance activities for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員performed maintenance tasks for B客戶on a specific date.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is providing maintenance services for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;A人员负责处理B客户的维护记录。&lt;SEP&gt;#A人員provided maintenance and support services for B客戶's systems.</data>
  <data key="d9">client relationship,client-engineer,engineering service,handling engineer,maintenance,maintenance activity,maintenance record,maintenance service,maintenance task,service,service provision,support,technical support</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
