  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="B客戶" target="C人員">
  <data key="d7">15.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relationship between (B客户, C人员) describes the connection where personnel (C人员) provide various maintenance and technical support services to customers (B客户). Specifically, C人员 are responsible for conducting regular maintenance activities to ensure that B客户的 systems or equipment operate smoothly and efficiently. This includes addressing specific technical issues as they arise, providing ongoing support, and implementing targeted solutions to maintain optimal system performance. The relationship encompasses a wide range of maintenance tasks aimed at keeping B客户的 operations running seamlessly, with C人员 playing a critical role in troubleshooting and enhancing the reliability of B客户的 systems. Additionally, C人员 handle maintenance issues on an ongoing basis and are involved in the overall maintenance and support of B客户的 system assets.</data>
  <data key="d9">client-engineer,client-engineer relationship,engineering service,handling engineer,maintenance,maintenance activity,maintenance record,maintenance service,maintenance support,responsibility,service provision,support,technical support</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-412e17859c430b9ce8b929bc152053ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0d3b88d3601a1081c8354e0ef27952f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6e1908b68b82814f06780675f7938b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39206ec5906f23d68e051b1df74d3ca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c3e0271089b72556be831ea38a055f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5</data>
