<edge source="C人員" target="E客戶">
  <data key="d7">18.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(C人员, E客户) refers to a professional relationship where C人员 provides maintenance and service activities for E客户. This relationship is characterized by regular maintenance service provision by C人员 to ensure the smooth operation of E客户的 systems. The services provided include system maintenance tasks that are crucial for ensuring the correct and efficient functioning of systems used by E客户.

C人员 has been responsible for performing these maintenance services on multiple occasions, including December 4th, 2025, and December 9th, 2025. These maintenance activities encompass a range of tasks related to system upkeep at E客户的 location, all documented in service records maintained by C人员. Specifically, C人员 handles the maintenance for E客户, performing various tasks as required and ensuring that work content is accurately recorded.

C人员 provides maintenance support involving multiple tasks such as troubleshooting issues, updating systems, and conducting routine checks. The detailed documentation of these activities ensures transparency and accountability within the relationship between C人员 and E客户. Overall, this professional relationship emphasizes the importance of consistent and thorough maintenance service to sustain efficient system operation for E客户.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶receives technical support and maintenance services provided by C人員.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員provides maintenance and support services to E客戶as part of their operational responsibilities.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員provides maintenance services for E客戶's site-based work items.</data>
  <data key="d9">client-engineer,client-engineer interaction,client-engineer relationship,customer-engineer relationship,customer-technician relationship,maintenance,maintenance record,maintenance service,maintenance support,maintenance work,service provider,service provision,technical service</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-c0c6684aa00106f16e7869f519061642&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76068a2f95fd89e7ceb4741d4eb478ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d02e98febcd8f8650bbe77d789a41d69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25d7c29d65aa0e4d54fb4af54207fa0d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a40e782f3c3804da0a1d45dfa05eefe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-738a58105cbf665748b3257e0cfee9ac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0add79f46581b83deba682a2c89cdb7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcc4bf66788ce00c23c3e736753ea50a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5096c0cdf6972a3670732e4f9be1d36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0cef05272158ef916c2b84f625b2ddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1df6d8d113790f99d50593095e1e5e58&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bddb98b4a84e394c0a4558b42ae12d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0cd3e323fc2a43e461d7af757b08706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cafeb58d25cc4cbc85eaf07cf415496a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0640212d45b4b92d91d0255cf90edf96&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6f1e5469f6278ea8a34bff96b293b69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-996c8aba3ce4de0e9bb90c0d569231f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6839b81653aa7c9b7ec794f3447380</data>
