<edge source="Market Selloff" target="Nexon Technologies">
  <data key="d7">12.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The term "Market Selloff, Nexon Technologies" refers to a period during which Nexon Technologies' stock performance was notably affected by wider market trends. The decline in Nexon Technologies' stock price is closely linked to broader market dynamics characterized by investor concerns over rising interest rates and regulatory uncertainties. These factors created an environment of heightened economic uncertainty that negatively impacted the company's financial performance, leading to a significant drop in its stock value. Consequently, Nexon Technologies' own financial struggles further contributed to and reinforced broader investor anxieties during this period, creating a feedback loop that exacerbated the overall market selloff.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies' stock decline is part of the broader market selloff driven by investor concerns over interest rates and regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies' stock decline contributed to the broader market selloff driven by investor concerns.&lt;SEP&gt;The decline in Nexon Technologies' stock is influenced by broader concerns about market conditions and regulatory uncertainty.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies' poor earnings report contributed to overall negative investor sentiment during the market selloff.</data>
  <data key="d9">company impact,company performance,economic concern,economic environment,economic factors,index movement,investor sentiment,market performance,market reaction</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-203eba714089c79438cfc39755f054ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7743e93210e95e8e40e0d2a627684b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07959bdb8bab221c9c80a1c3e85776b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cdd29ae3537f38a27c3848632ad51359&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0add79f46581b83deba682a2c89cdb7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d3d3acb3c191c9e65fac21b5ed9284f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2fe3f974e54dd1f1ad98289cc79980d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c41e50d3a458388dc7fe53ece68ee69f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518</data>
