<edge source="C客戶" target="B人員">
  <data key="d7">18.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B人员, C客户) represents a relationship where B人员 are responsible for providing maintenance services to C客户. This includes handling and recording maintenance activities on behalf of C客户. Specifically, B人员 perform various maintenance tasks, manage maintenance records, and ensure that all necessary services are provided during the specified time period. Their duties encompass both the execution of maintenance work and the documentation required to track these activities effectively for C客户. Additionally, B人员 provided maintenance services related to Splunk SH systems for C客户, further illustrating their comprehensive role in maintaining and servicing systems on behalf of C客户.&lt;SEP&gt;B人员is assigned to provide maintenance services for C客户.&lt;SEP&gt;B人员为C客户提供维护服务。&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is responsible for performing maintenance services for C客戶.</data>
  <data key="d9">client-engineer relationship,engineer assignment,engineer responsibility,engineer-client relationship,maintenance,maintenance service,maintenance support,maintenance work,responsibility,service provider,service provision,support</data>
